sub_title: Freelance Writer at Words With Dani
summary: I've turned my love of creative writing into a job! I can be either short and to the point or I can create long-form content as well. My educational background means I am an excellent fit for projects oriented toward governmental, international, and/or non-profit sectors. I work well on rails, with full creativity, and everywhere in between. Fast turnaround times and I am quick to reply to communication.
